	   <tr><td colspan=2>Although pets are probably fine at lower levels, once you get into higher levels your pets are awful, for the simple fact that you can not control them.&nbsp;&nbsp;If you are in a group and you are in the middle of mezzing something, and it hits you once, your pet will destroy your mez.  As a 38 chanter I haven't created a pet in over 20 levels.  Although if you fear kite that works to have a pet too.  Enchant spells are good to have for extra money but not necessary<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
